Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.00,0:06:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.08,0:06:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.17,0:06:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.25,0:06:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.33,0:06:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.75,0:06:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我点提示
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.88,0:06:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“人形”的弱点是?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.59,0:06:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头上的环
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.67,0:06:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头上的环
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头上的环
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.84,0:06:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头上的环
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.92,0:06:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头上的环
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头上的环
